Near Clemmons / Mile Marker 182 to 182 Heading West. The Contractor for the I-0911A project (I-40 over the Yadkin River at the Davie-Forsyth County Line) plans&nbsp;to close a ramp at Exit 182 (Harper Road) near Clemmons on Wednesday September 30th. The contractor will close the on-ramp from Harper Road to I-40 westbound overnight from 10:00PM - 6:00AM. A detour will be utilized for this ramp closure. A link to the detour map is provided below. The contractor will utilize this ramp closure to safely perform work on the noise wall adjacent to the ramp.This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
